des: Tibetan Bowl sounds are therapeutic, calming, and meditative. Get started by saying, 'Alexa, open Tibetan Bowl Sounds,' and enjoy a 30-minute session of sound. It's an excellent feature to use during sleep, for deep relaxation, meditation practices, or to help concentrate on your tasks.
